  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/1c396d18b8157a0b58ce3792a9a8d584.avif?t=1746093364\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras_big/1c396d18b8157a0b58ce3792a9a8d584.avif?t=1746093364 width=800 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you wake up, you suddenly find yourself back in time, you have a vague memory, you don't know why you are here, and in the process of escaping, you may discover the truth hidden behind this place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/d6d25ef023da29356fc74dd6fecbff97.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=688 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game requires players to explore different scenarios to trigger and find out different events and solve the mysteries around them step by step</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/813a4036e4871951cbaade34c0f809fc.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the same time, it is also necessary to pay attention to the different people around you, talk to them to find out what the problem is, and require the player to judge right and wrong</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/8eb81d4f53b0be1811de5fcec0816dbf.avif?t=1746093364\" width=740 height=1002 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also a variety of events and texts for the player to explore, which will help the player understand that they are in the world and influence their choices, and escape from it step by step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/658196243d2f46f55e279a76443d7f6e.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player's choice will lead to the triggering of different endings, and it is irreversible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/4065ac00f57687c223b46d0acc937efa.avif?t=1746093364\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras_big/4065ac00f57687c223b46d0acc937efa.avif?t=1746093364 width=800 height=494 /></span>Players will also have to be careful as they explore and watch out for monster chases, which will tear apart your spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/272ae11e2d9a87ed4e767d08a8f568e0.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player also pays attention to the changes that occur in the scene in order to find a way out</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/1c396d18b8157a0b58ce3792a9a8d584.avif?t=1746093364\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras_big/1c396d18b8157a0b58ce3792a9a8d584.avif?t=1746093364 width=800 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you wake up, you suddenly find yourself back in time, you have a vague memory, you don't know why you are here, and in the process of escaping, you may discover the truth hidden behind this place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/d6d25ef023da29356fc74dd6fecbff97.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=688 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game requires players to explore different scenarios to trigger and find out different events and solve the mysteries around them step by step</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/813a4036e4871951cbaade34c0f809fc.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the same time, it is also necessary to pay attention to the different people around you, talk to them to find out what the problem is, and require the player to judge right and wrong</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/8eb81d4f53b0be1811de5fcec0816dbf.avif?t=1746093364\" width=740 height=1002 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also a variety of events and texts for the player to explore, which will help the player understand that they are in the world and influence their choices, and escape from it step by step.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/658196243d2f46f55e279a76443d7f6e.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player's choice will lead to the triggering of different endings, and it is irreversible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/4065ac00f57687c223b46d0acc937efa.avif?t=1746093364\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras_big/4065ac00f57687c223b46d0acc937efa.avif?t=1746093364 width=800 height=494 /></span>Players will also have to be careful as they explore and watch out for monster chases, which will tear apart your spirit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3649610/extras/272ae11e2d9a87ed4e767d08a8f568e0.avif?t=1746093364\" width=800 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player also pays attention to the changes that occur in the scene in order to find a way out</p>",
